  "title": "Fullstack Developer (React/Python)",
  "description": "<h3><strong>Job Summary:</strong></h3>\n<p>We are seeking a skilled and motivated <strong>Full Stack Developer</strong> with strong experience in modern frontend and backend technologies. The ideal candidate will have a solid foundation in <strong>React (Next.js)</strong> and/or <strong>Vue.js</strong>, combined with backend development experience using <strong>Python (FastAPI)</strong> and <strong>PostgreSQL</strong>. Familiarity with <strong>custom API integrations</strong> is a must. Exposure to <strong>Java</strong> for selective modules is a plus.</p>\n<h3><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Develop and maintain scalable frontend applications using <strong>React (Next.js)</strong>, <strong>Vue.js</strong>, <strong>SCSS</strong>, and <strong>Ant Design (antd)</strong></li>\n  <li>Build and optimize backend APIs using <strong>Python (FastAPI)</strong> and integrate with <strong>PostgreSQL</strong></li>\n  <li>Work on custom API integrations with third-party services</li>\n  <li>Collaborate with UI/UX designers, backend engineers, and product managers to deliver high-quality features</li>\n  <li>Ensure cross-browser compatibility, responsiveness, and performance optimization</li>\n  <li>Troubleshoot and debug issues across the full stack</li>\n  <li>Write clean, maintainable, and well-documented code</li>\n  <li>Participate in code reviews and team discussions</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>Requirements:</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Strong experience with <strong>React (Next.js)</strong> and/or <strong>Vue.js</strong></li>\n  <li>Proficiency in <strong>SCSS</strong>, <strong>Ant Design (antd)</strong>, and responsive UI development</li>\n  <li>Solid experience in <strong>Python (FastAPI)</strong> and RESTful API development</li>\n  <li>Knowledge of <strong>PostgreSQL</strong> and database schema design</li>\n  <li>Experience with custom third-party API integrations</li>\n  <li>Good understanding of Git version control and Agile development practices</li>\n  <li>Strong problem-solving skills and attention to detail</li>\n  <li>Good communication and teamwork abilities</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>Nice to Have:</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Experience with <strong>uni-app</strong> for cross-platform development</li>\n  <li>Familiarity with <strong>Java</strong>, particularly in modular backend systems</li>\n  <li>Previous experience in performance tuning and security best practices</li>\n</ul>",
